data.description: Seller is willing to give $15,000 credit to help buy down interest rate, assist with closing cost, etc.     It doesn't get much better than this beautiful 10-acre horse property ready for your livestock with 7.88 acres of water rights. This property features a fully finished basement with a bathroom and two additional rooms, along with an enclosed winter greenhouse to continue your gardening in the colder months. Upgraded open kitchen with ample counter and cabinet space as well as a breakfast nook. Savor the Nevada sunsets under your private gazebo with a fireplace. The shop provides plentiful space for storage, to include a generator to supplying electricity.
